```

**Required Fields:**
- `openclaw.extensions`: Array of entry points (e.g., `["./index.ts"]`)
- `openclaw.setupEntry`: Path to setup-only entry point
- `openclaw.channel.id`: Must match `openclaw.plugin.json:id`
- `openclaw.channel.label`: Display name for UI

**Optional but Recommended:**
- `selectionLabel`: Custom label shown in selection UI
- `detailLabel`: Detail description
- `blurb`: Short help text
- `docsPath`: Link to documentation
- `markdownCapable`: Whether channel supports markdown formatting

