# OpenClaw Channel Plugin Exploration Report

## Executive Summary

I've explored the OpenClaw plugin architecture and identified the **Nostr plugin as a minimal but complete channel plugin template**. The Nostr plugin is simpler than many alternatives (Signal, IRC) yet demonstrates all required patterns.

